  "text": "DC based vaccines for patients with malignant diseases generated under different culture conditions have been investigated for more than a decade. Despite these efforts, clinical results of DC vaccination studies showed thera- peutic efficacy only in a limited number of patients so far [CITATION_1] . In search of an alternative way for DC generation we examined the molecular and functional characteristics of IFN-DC in comparison to IL-4/TNF-DC.",
